{"tid":675813,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[5月24日發售] 起哄音樂節","createTime":"2018-05-24T00:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-21T10:08:12.000Z","uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2e7491046452d1bab2c8e03b436c9bbaa099c57f","tid":675813,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T00:31:23.000Z","msg":"內容簡介<br />\n今個暑假，啟航娛樂集團舉辦三場全城狂呼，令樂迷耳目一新的起哄音樂節，延續夏日無限精彩！ <br />\n<br />\n第一場(8月24日)將會有久未與樂迷見面的Mr.及CHOCHUKMO (觸執毛)作開場；<br />\n第二場(8月25日)則有有ToNick、KOLOR及YELLOW!演出；<br />\n第三場就由台灣歌手丁噹、閻奕格及盧學叡為音樂節劃上完美句號。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkticketing.com/sistic/images/events/3771/1526551883987.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkticketing.com%2Fsistic%2Fimages%2Fevents%2F3771%2F1526551883987.gif&h=3fa239a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>開始售票日期</strong><br />\n2018年5月24日 (星期四) 上午10時<br />\n<strong>節目類別</strong><br />\n演唱會<br />\n<strong>節目查詢</strong><br />\n3118 7128<br />\n<strong>演出時間</strong><br />\n約180分鐘 (不設中場休息)<br />\n主辦機構名稱<br />\n啟航娛樂集團<br />\n<br />\n節目資料只供參考，主辦單位有權更改節目資料及時間表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkticketing.com/events/KBMUSIC0818\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkticketing.com%2Fevents%2FKBMUSIC0818&d=h5CBWGnPckCkRoAY9OKbop4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=a422dc04\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkticketing.com/events/KBMUSIC0818</a>"},{"pid":"7e9453b8d0ff6fcf5c183c2db6e6a2ac9028166d","tid":675813,"uid":96008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T00:51:13.000Z","msg":"Mr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a50bf5529dcfdbf1f9f7ff303c9049c31402af7","tid":675813,"uid":181939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T00:58:45.000Z","msg":"Kolor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"