\n<br />\n2017年Mr.以&ldquo;Mister Forever&rdquo;為主題在廣州開始內地巡演，音樂會中透過音樂，將現實生活的正反面帶出，教人樂觀積極面對，並與樂迷一起感悟，一起搖滾，一起吶喊。<br />\n<br />\n在內地巡演廣州站，深圳站，東莞站，亞運城，佛山站之後，音樂會特別來到澳門舉行。他們證明了不管多少年過去，仍然用心做音樂，一步一步向前走，這就是Mr.搭建的森林。Mr.以全新音樂創出新態度，回饋歌迷。<br />\n<br />\n日期<br />\n2018年6月30日<br />\n位置<br />\n百老匯舞台<br />\n價格<br />\nVIP880／680／480／280<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.broadwaymacau.com.mo/zh-hant/macau-entertainment/now-showing/mister-live-concert2018\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.broadwaymacau.com.mo%2Fzh-hant%2Fmacau-entertainment%2Fnow-showing%2Fmister-live-concert2018&d=h5CBWGnPckCkRoAY9OKbop4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f0f15f3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.broadwaymacau.com.mo/zh-hant/macau-entertainment/now-showing/mister-live-concert2018</a>"},{"pid":"c99979fc4ecedc447763908c890a9d21fdcb2c5b","tid":675813,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"009bf9adcfd2e4ab444013c65df9ea5a22ebb7d9","tid":675813,"uid":19208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fc375bf2165a31a0697ab40496027b0b72216b68","tid":675813,"uid":26773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:02:22.000Z","msg":"想睇mr<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:10:42.000Z","msg":"想睇MR, 不如去睇呢個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong>MISTER FOREVER 狂熱音樂會 澳門站</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.broadwaymacau.com.mo/uploads/attachment/2018-05/979825ae98816eb781.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.broadwaymacau.com.mo%2Fuploads%2Fattachment%2F2018-05%2F979825ae98816eb781.jpg&h=1732c49e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2017年Mr.以&ldquo;Mister Forever&rdquo;為主題在廣州開始內地巡演，音樂會中透過音樂，將現實生活的正反面帶出，教人樂觀積極面對，並與樂迷一起感悟，一起搖滾，一起吶喊。<br />\n<br />\n在內地巡演廣州站，深圳站，東莞站，亞運城，佛山站之後，音樂會特別來到澳門舉行。他們證明了不管多少年過去，仍然用心做音樂，一步一步向前走，這就是Mr.搭建的森林。Mr.以